        "name": "Retrospective observational study of clinical VAD registry",
        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "description": "Retrospective extraction and analysis of de-identified haemolysis biomarker data from a multi-site VAD implant registry. Operating-condition metadata (pump speed, flow rate) were obtained from device logs. No experimental manipulation of variables was performed; data were collected as part of routine clinical monitoring. Statistical harmonisation across sites was applied to account for assay differences.",
        "startedAtTime": "2025-06-01T00:00:00Z",
        "endedAtTime": "2025-11-30T00:00:00Z",
        "wasAssociatedWith": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/vad-clinical-consortium"
